transcript:
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haanji sir, whatsapp pe maine bhej diya hai aapko link, aapne dekha?
Executive: Ek minute, ek minute.
Customer: Haan, ek baar dekh lijiye aur forward kar lijiye.
Customer: Aur main aapko whatsapp call bhi kar rahi thi kal, but aapka lag nahi raha tha whatsapp call.
Executive: Nahi, woh thoda issue chal raha hai na woh iska wajah se. Ek minute, main aapko whatsapp call hi kar raha hu.
Customer: Ji ji kariye aap.
summary:
Concerns:

- Link sent on WhatsApp not viewed.

- WhatsApp call not connecting.



Resolution:

- Executive to check the link sent on WhatsApp and forward it.

- Executive to make a WhatsApp call to the customer.



Next Steps: 

Issue not resolved. Executive will call back on WhatsApp.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

Neutral to Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

whatsapp link, whatsapp call
